questionnaireMod-questionnaire.html:
1) Do you worry about taxonomical aspect of the data?


2) What is the lowest taxonomic level you require in your data?


3) Do you worry about spatial aspect of the data?


4) What is the spatial resolution required for your data? (in meteres)


5) Do you worry about precision of coordinates?


6) Do you worry about countries of occurrences?


7) Do you worry about temporal aspect of your data?


8) What is the range of dates of the observations in this data set? In format (YYYY-mm-dd YYYY-mm-dd)

to

9) What temporal resolution are you interested in?


10) Do you worry about dates other than occured date (published date/identified date)?


11) Do you worry about other properties of occurrence? (GBIF issues/publisher/occuranceremark, etc)?
